com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.dataobject

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.dataobject.AbstractRecord
      • com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.dataobject.Result
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Result
extends AbstractRecord
implements Serializable
    Result is an abstraction of result of a back-end service call. Result is a collection of Params, Datasets and Records.
    See Also:
    Param, Dataset, Record, Serialized Form

      • removeParam

        public void removeParam(Param param)
        Removes the given Param from the Param list of the Result. This method shouldn't be used while iterating over the Params of the Result, as removing while iterating may throw ConcurrentModificationException.
        Parameters:
        param - The Param to remove
        See Also:
        Param
